\id PHM - Mufian NT (Balif dialect) -Papua New Guinea 1988 (web version -2013 bd) 
\h Filemoni 
\toc1 Basef Ifimba Pol Nandaꞌef Fagafeꞌma Filemoni 
\toc2 Fagafeꞌma Filemoni 
\toc3 Fm 
\mt1 Basef Ifimba Pol Nandaꞌef Fagafeꞌma Filemoni  
\iot Basef bandafi Pol nandaꞌef fagafeꞌma Filemoni  
\io1 1-3 Pol naꞌipa Filemon basef buꞌwafi ma God noloma Jisas Krais mogatopalopana  
\io1 4-7 Pol nanifela Goda Filemon nandabetenana  
\io1 8-22 Pol nahaliꞌ Filemona nogatopalopa Onesimus  
\io1 23-25 Basef akutaifi faloma dagala Poli  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Aeꞌ Pol, aeꞌ andaꞌ kalabusa maol Krais Jisasi. Owamafa afaꞌinai Timoti nape nalome naꞌaꞌe.  
\p Eaꞌ andaꞌ basef ifimba fafeꞌmago inaꞌ Filemon, alipunai afaꞌinai ma wandaꞌ maol atin Godi. Ukup afaꞌipi paipailina aꞌowaꞌ.\x * \xo 1:1 \xt Kl 4:17; 2 Ti 2:3; Ef 3:1\x*  
\v 2 Aeꞌ andaꞌ basef ifimba ma inaꞌ naloma amam nematawa Godi sandakolas ipat ineꞌitai saloma hanitiꞌmafa Apia kwaloma aman anamba Arkipus, nandaꞌ maol Godi banagambel siꞌi soldia naloma afaꞌ biafa.\x * \xo 1:2 \xt Ga 1:3\x*   
\p
\v 3 Aeꞌ aꞌi ahamapa God noloma Dembinai apeꞌinai Jisas Krais amom motopalopepa dowaf mowaꞌ banagaepa mondaꞌ opalef ipeꞌilifi fepe awanelef.\x * \xo 1:3 \xt Ro 1:8-9\x*   
\s1 Filemon aꞌ nahapifa dembinai Jisas eaꞌ okom ananimi maimaila epes hiasi Godi  
\p
\v 4 Dondol aeꞌ anifela Goda nimaguf hiafi aꞌi agol ineꞌigili andabeten.  
\v 5 Deiꞌ main, aeꞌ ameꞌasa inaꞌ nahapifa dembinai Jisas endilisi eaꞌ okom ineꞌimi maimaila amam nematawa Godi hiasi hiꞌalas.\x * \xo 1:5 \xt Fl 1:9; Kl 1:9\x*  
\v 6 Aeꞌ andabeten ahaliꞌ God aꞌi inaꞌ niꞌipasa hapif ineꞌini kofagena newaꞌ banaga anis daias. Inaꞌ nendaꞌas naꞌamba ma negegawa andeandeꞌ hiahaom buꞌwami apaꞌ magape sisihipama Kraisi mogofaꞌami.\x * \xo 1:6 \xt 2 Ko 7:4\x*  
\v 7 Owame aeꞌinai, inaꞌ okom maimaila amam nematawa Godi ma negewaꞌ banaga opalef asasilifi. Eaꞌ aeꞌ sonahemena aꞌowaꞌ ma waf afamba ineꞌifi eaꞌ fewaꞌ banaga opaf aeꞌafi awanef aꞌowaꞌ.   
\s1 Pol naꞌi Filemon aꞌ nofaꞌai Onesimus notanimai siꞌi epen Godi  
\p
\v 8 Eaꞌ okom aeꞌami maꞌi naꞌamba. Endilisi, aeꞌ ape aposel banagewe ma agol Kraisi igaꞌipina dindinipa nendaꞌ anef waf usiꞌifi.\x * \xo 1:8 \xt Fm 1\x*  
\v 9 Apaꞌ aeꞌ andaiwaꞌ ma igaꞌipina dindinip, owaꞌ. God okom maimailafa eaꞌ afaꞌ wapani ukup paipaila epes hiasi. Isimba atis deiꞌ ahaliꞌina. Aeꞌ Pol, hagewe eaꞌ deiꞌ ape andaꞌ kalabus andaꞌ maol Krais Jisasi,\x * \xo 1:9 \xt Kl 4:9; 1 Ko 4:15\x*  
\v 10 aeꞌ ahaliꞌina ma nogame aeꞌanai Onesimus. Inaꞌ niti anen uwahipina. Nogota atamba ape andaꞌ kalabus, aeꞌ aꞌipana basef Godi. Eaꞌ nahapifa Krais aꞌ nataga nogame aeꞌanai.  
\v 11 Fowaꞌ anen ina nandaꞌ maol buꞌwani ma inaꞌ, owaꞌatin. Eaꞌ nandaiwaꞌmana. Apaꞌ deiꞌ aꞌ laꞌifina ma nondaꞌ maol buꞌwani ma nogatopalopa afaꞌ biafa.   
\p
\v 12 Deiꞌ aeꞌ esapaꞌana notambel nefeꞌmago inaꞌ. Eaꞌ okom aeꞌami mefeꞌ molomanago.\x * \xo 1:12 \xt Fl 2:30\x*  
\v 13 Aeꞌ andaꞌ maol awalipasa basef buꞌwafi Godi eaꞌ sandaꞌe andaꞌ kalabus. Eaꞌ aeꞌ aꞌi elaꞌata Onesimus nope naꞌa nolome atapina nohoꞌofena ma nogatopalope.\x * \xo 1:13 \xt 2 Ko 9:7; 1 Pi 5:2\x*  
\v 14 Apaꞌ iꞌi inaꞌ nindaiwaꞌma elaꞌatana nope nogalome ma, hapainai. Aeꞌ andaiwaꞌma igaꞌipina dindinip. Aeꞌ aꞌi inaꞌ niꞌi ahoꞌma okom ineꞌimi atoma anen nope nogalome.  
\v 15 Onesimus aꞌ nakwahina nogota bandata nafeꞌ anagona bola nefaꞌana notanimai nope nolomena lifilafi dondol.\x * \xo 1:15 \xt 1 Ti 6:2\x*  
\v 16 Eaꞌ deiꞌ anen ina ataꞌ nagape lafela anis epes agol akanai, owaꞌatin. Anen aꞌ nataga owamena endilisi ma Krais dondoꞌma ukup pigapigailana endilisi. Ahoꞌ aeꞌ okom maimailana. Apaꞌ inaꞌ atiasi okom mimilana aꞌowaꞌ, niꞌi owamena ineꞌinai ma agol Dembinaii.  
\v 17 Iꞌi inaꞌ okom mondandaꞌma aeꞌ niꞌi afaꞌ wandaoꞌoma endilisi wandaꞌ maol Kraisi, daoꞌ aꞌ andeandeꞌma inaꞌ nefaꞌ Onesimus notanimago sonehenamana siꞌi naꞌi negefaꞌ aeꞌ.  
\v 18 Iꞌi anen nondaꞌ anef waf awafi ma inaꞌ aꞌa nondaꞌmena anof wiaf fopomena, daoꞌ aeꞌ egwamonaf.\x * \xo 1:18 \xt 1 Ko 16:21; Ga 6:11\x*   
\p
\v 19 Deiꞌ aeꞌ Pol ahapila pen lagol aeꞌagili atogol andaꞌ basef ifimba bandafi atif, aeꞌ atiasi egwamona wiaf afamba.  
\p Endilisi inaꞌ wapani nape siꞌi aꞌ negewaola anof wiafa aeꞌ. Wiaf afamba ina siꞌi otamba mais, owaꞌatin. Afamba ambal ineꞌili atol. Deiꞌ main, fowaꞌ aꞌipina basef buꞌwafi nahapifif nefaꞌ ambal namili nape andeandeꞌ.  
\v 20 Eaꞌ owame alipinai, aeꞌ ihaliꞌina ma agol Dembinaii, inaꞌ ninifela Onesimus siꞌi owamena nagahapifa Kraisi. Afaꞌ sahin owan wagahapifa Kraisi atofa. Eaꞌ inaꞌ nendaꞌ opaf aeꞌafi fotaga boꞌof newaꞌ banagai sonehe.   
\p
\v 21 Andaꞌ basef ifimba, aꞌ egawa endilisi inaꞌ atiasi nigaila basef ifimba aeꞌafii. Eaꞌ aeꞌ deiꞌ andaꞌago basef ifimba ma inaꞌ. Eaꞌ egawa anif basef wapani, inaꞌ atiasi nendaꞌ anef waf buꞌwafi endilisi fikilaꞌ isimba deiꞌ aꞌipina pas isiꞌi aꞌi inaꞌ nendaꞌasi.\x * \xo 1:21 \xt Fl 1:25, 2:24\x*  
\v 22 Eaꞌ anif basef wapani. Aeꞌ okom mandandaꞌ aꞌi God atiasi nemeꞌ beten ipeꞌini nokwaha aeꞌ efeꞌmago ipaꞌ wapani. Eaꞌ deiꞌ inaꞌ nendondomba anagon nopomago ma aeꞌ efoꞌo epe egalomena.\x * \xo 1:22 \xt Kl 1:7\x*   
\s1 Anis sasapaꞌago dagala asasini  
\p
\v 23 Epafras anen nape nandaꞌ kalabus naloma aeꞌ ma agol Krais Jisasi. Anen nandaꞌmenago dagala nefeꞌ nelomago inaꞌ.\x * \xo 1:23 \xt Kl 4:10,14; 1 Ti 4:10-11\x*  
\v 24 Eaꞌ amom mandaꞌ maol magalumai, Mak naloma Aristarkusi Demasi Luk, amom wapani mandaꞌmenago dagala inaꞌ.   
\p
\v 25 Aeꞌ aꞌi Dembinai Jisas Krais netopalopepa dowaf nowaꞌ banagaipa ma waf afamba fepe felomago ambagufi ukup ipaꞌ hipaii. Eaꞌ maꞌuf.   